title: Person of Interest: Reese VS Assassins
author: POI Fights
comment: This episode is great! I'm re-watching it right now. And I miss the fight scenes like this. Reese is the best and Caviezel is perfect :D Anyway, thank you for uploading all the fight scenes.

Thumbs-UP #69 I am, Sunday’s early afternoon 23 December 2018!  I like how John turns around, looks sternly at the woman assassin and just says “guess the honeymoons over”.  The Flight Attendant’s “oops” is a funny addition. 😆
2 assasins against reece a trained killer not fair odds for them.

John Wick, John Rambo, Elliot Spencer, Robert McCall, Casey Ryback, JJMcQuade, Kwai Chang Caine, Mike Banning, Christian Wolff, Jason Bourne, John Reese and Frank Moses walk into a bar ....... Who walks out?
